Subject: The Brown Liquors
Description: What's the difference between Bourbon and Scotch? Is Tennessee whiskey any different from Irish? How? Why? Come hear how these different 'Brown Liquors' are made, and what makes them unique from one another. And while your at it, find out for yourself by sampling a little of each.Must be 21+ to participate. Spots are limited - please sign up at Ops!  Speakers include:Greg Williams, Karen Corbeill, James Gamble - Track: Food  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
